items.sentence: Tom didn't like swimming when he was younger.
I saw Tom and Mary holding hands in the park.
I don't believe that I can do that by myself.
Tom is aware the police are looking for Mary.
Tom realized Mary might not like him so much.
Did you find the person you were looking for?
You walk on and I'll catch up with you later.
You can't seriously want me to sell my house.
You can't let them take my kids away from me.
You can't really shoot your own dog, can you?
